31 (ii) The national motto shall:
32 (a) Be easily readable on a poster or framed
33 copy of at least eleven inches by fourteen inches (11″ x 14″);
34 (b) Be the central focus of the poster or
35 framed copy; and.
36 (c) Be displayed in a large font size;.
